snippet.title: Version 2.3 Trailer: "Farewell, Penacony" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
The trailblazing expedition of Penacony has come to a wonderful conclusion. It's time to stride forward to the next destination — but before moving on, let's bid a formal farewell to the white night behind you.

English Voice:
Firefly & SAM — Analesa Fisher & Adin Rudd
Sparkle — Lizzie Freeman
Jade — Faye Mata
Robin — Alice Himora
Screwllum — Steven Kelly
